commit_list.repo_description: Our project seeks to reduce food waste in Chicago by connecting restaurants, cafes, and individuals that produce food waste with nearby urban farms and community gardens accepting compostable material. Locations with composting programs can use our site to post their information, and businesses and individuals with compostable material can search for nearby composting programs to get in touch with.
